{"kind":"overview","hierarchy":{"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","paths":[]},"sections":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Discovering a new framework can be exciting and scary. Learn how you can embed and use OUDS Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"With this tutorial you will learn fundamental concepts of Orange Unified Design System and discover the layers of this framework.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Theme, components, tokens… everything will be introduced!","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"hero","title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","backgroundImage":"ic_unified_ds.png","action":{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Get started","type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get started"}]},"image":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"content":[],"kind":"volume","image":null,"chapters":[{"name":"Import of the Swift Package and choose its librairies","image":"ic_unified_ds.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In this chapter you will learn how to import the OUDS iOS Swift Package and which librairies it provides","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you should choose for your needs.","type":"text"}]}],"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies"]},{"name":"Preparation of the theme","image":"ic_theme_intro.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will see how to instanciate a theme and inject it inside your app"}]}],"tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme"]},{"name":"Use of first components provided by OUDS","image":"ic_component_intro.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inli